== Ubuntu & Debian

sudo apt-get install libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev zlib1g-dev ruby1.8-dev build-essential ruby ruby1.8 rubygems
sudo gem install ruby-xml-smart (>= 0.2.1.1 needed)
sudo gem install rack mongrel mime-types
sudo gem install activesupport

For websocket support you need a custom rack gem. 
  * http://www.pri.univie.ac.at/~mangler/rack-1.1.0+rack.io.gem
  * deinstall all other rack stuff, for less problems
  * todo make the io patch a rack monkey patch addon

